#3
"""Logging configuration to be set for the server"""
LOGGER_NAME: str = 'marketplace'
LOG_FORMAT: str = '%(levelprefix)s | %(asctime)s | %(message)s'
LOG_LEVEL: str = 'DEBUG'
version: int = 1
disable_existing_loggers: bool = False
formatters: dict = {'default': {'()': 'uvicorn.logging.DefaultFormatter',
    'fmt': LOG_FORMAT, 'datefmt': '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'}}
handlers: dict = {'default': {'formatter': 'default', 'class':
    'logging.StreamHandler', 'stream': 'ext://sys.stderr'}}
loggers: dict = {LOGGER_NAME: {'handlers': ['default'], 'level': LOG_LEVEL}}
